l! Always kept our glasses full, checked in on us often but not to much, he was extremely professional, well mannered just an all around great guy!   So in conclusion even though service was not what we expected the food more than made up for it!  Maybe just a bad day for our server, we all have them. But next time we are in Las Vegas we will definitely be going back to GR Steak!!
